We are delighted that you
have agreed to kick it off

00:26:10.450 --> 00:26:14.610
and actually read right here

00:26:14.610 --> 00:26:17.810
and start the Imagination
Library story time

00:26:17.810 --> 00:26:19.150
at the Library of Congress.

