I recall a box of rags
that someone gave us

00:27:49.040 --> 00:27:53.210
and how my momma put
those rags to use.

00:27:53.210 --> 00:27:57.910
There were rags of many colors
but every piece was small.

00:27:57.910 --> 00:28:02.450
I didn't have a coat and it
was way down in the fall.

00:28:02.450 --> 00:28:06.900
So momma sewed the rags
together, she sewed every piece

00:28:06.900 --> 00:28:10.320
with love and made my
coat of many colors

00:28:10.320 --> 00:28:13.210
that I was so proud of.

00:28:13.210 --> 00:28:18.060
As momma sewed she told a story
from the Bible she had read

00:28:18.060 --> 00:28:22.420
about a coat of many colors
Joseph wore and then she said,

00:28:22.420 --> 00:28:26.630
I hope this coat will bring
you good luck and happiness.

00:28:26.630 --> 00:28:29.020
And I couldn't wait to wear it,

00:28:29.020 --> 00:28:31.460
and momma blessed
it with a kiss.

00:28:31.460 --> 00:28:37.140
So with patches on my britches
and holes in both my shoes,

00:28:37.140 --> 00:28:41.130
in my coat of many colors
I hurried off to school.

00:28:41.130 --> 00:28:46.040
Just to find the others laughing
and making fun of me in my coat

00:28:46.040 --> 00:28:49.630
of many colors that
momma made for me.

00:28:49.630 --> 00:28:55.200
In my coat of many colors
that my momma made for me,

00:28:55.200 --> 00:29:00.610
made only from rags but
I wore it so proudly!

00:29:00.610 --> 00:29:06.210
Although we had no money,
I was rich as I could be,

00:29:06.210 --> 00:29:12.100
in my coat of many
colors momma made for me.

00:29:12.100 --> 00:29:17.230
