because I felt I was rich!

00:29:33.770 --> 00:29:38.450
I told 'em of the love
momma sewed in every stitch.

00:29:38.450 --> 00:29:42.950
I even told 'em all that story
momma told me while she sewed

00:29:42.950 --> 00:29:46.830
and why my coat of many
colors was worth more

00:29:46.830 --> 00:29:48.240
than all their clothes.

00:29:48.240 --> 00:29:54.150
But they didn't understand it
and I tried to make them see

00:29:54.150 --> 00:29:59.580
that one is only poor
only if they choose to be.

00:29:59.580 --> 00:30:03.420
It's true we had no money,
but I was rich as I could be

00:30:03.420 --> 00:30:11.050
in my coat of many
colors momma made for me.

00:30:11.050 --> 00:30:26.130
'Cuz momma made it just for me.

